0.9.name: wordpress/tweet-map
0.9.description: The Tweet Map plugin provides shortcode to display your geo tagged Twitter tweets on a customizable Google map. Your pictures uploaded to twitter, twitpic, twitgoo, and yfrog will be display in the map's info window. The plugin runs on a hourly wordpress cron to keep your tweets up to date. Just use [tweet-map /] on any post or page to see a map of your tweets.
